{"tid":125671,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食一碗鴨瀨有感","createTime":"2017-02-18T16:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T17:03:07.000Z","uid":31962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"daed7a60a933c63baf0442484161d23531cd6088","tid":125671,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"下午茶係美心叫左碗鴨瀨，有啲想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先以前有燒鵝瀨的，唔知幾時起冇左...<br />\n鴨瀨之前點都係有條菜跟的，又唔知起幾時冇左...<br />\n連師父切野既木針板都冇左，換左舊膠...<br />\n習慣左真係好恐怖...<br />\n7警打人案個官已經判左，唔滿意咪上訴囉，遊戲係點玩唔駛講，但一班人既價值觀真係好奇怪...算喇習慣就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa3c757901bae9148eb8af573dcd46af406b27e","tid":125671,"uid":27356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"你講乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efc0616cfb810303d8ca6c8f6ed2178b6912899","tid":125671,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"中二病發作"},{"pid":"367f70852a293ec6380598dbbb39ffe5644b3552","tid":125671,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"先唔理你想暗示乜鳩 但講開美心鴨瀨我真係屌佢老味 將一舊正常size鴨胸肉打橫切三刀變三舊 食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"674a1c3a2eef23230a6ab0a524bc36673771197a","tid":125671,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n野食貴左 質素差左 香港人生活環境都差左 只係唔覺唔覺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6f766f3af4cab6449f6f7e64f635a2cce2dc48","tid":125671,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先唔理你想暗示乜鳩 但講開美心鴨瀨我真係屌佢老味 將一舊正常size鴨